      <title>据称 Arcapita 正在考虑上市中东房地产资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/arcapita-is-said-to-weigh-listing-middle-east-real-estate-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，另类投资公司 Arcapita Group Holdings 正在考虑设立一家房地产投资信托基金来投资其中东房地产资产。]]></description>
