    <item>
      <title>Race Capital：DeepSeek 为硅谷敲响警钟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-28/race-capital-deepseek-a-wake-up-call-for-silicon-valley-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[早期风险投资基金 Race Capital 的普通合伙人 Edith Yeung 表示，DeepSeek 让硅谷投资者对他们的 AI 投资产生了疑问。她在“彭博社：中国秀”节目中与 David Ingles 和 Stephen Engle 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-28/race-capital-deepseek-a-wake-up-call-for-silicon-valley-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 05:42:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦央行行长称，物价宽松为降息提供了空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/pakistan-s-easing-prices-gives-room-for-rate-cuts-governor-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦央行行长表示，通胀趋缓为放松货币政策提供了“充足空间”，而就在前一天，该行行长刚刚将基准利率下调至近三年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/pakistan-s-easing-prices-gives-room-for-rate-cuts-governor-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 05:41:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着股市暴跌持续，印度小型股指数进入熊市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/india-s-smallcap-stock-index-plunges-20-from-september-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度股市长达数月的抛售毫无减弱的迹象，小型股指数周二暴跌，从 9 月份的高点跌至 20%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/india-s-smallcap-stock-index-plunges-20-from-september-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 04:35:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能行业动荡导致比特币下跌，为加密货币涨势蒙上阴影</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/bitcoin-btc-drop-fueled-by-deepseek-ai-shakeup-spurs-doubts-over-crypto-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由中国人工智能初创公司 DeepSeek 引发的全球市场动荡导致了数字资产的波动，继去年价格暴涨之后，人们对加密货币的前景产生了新的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/bitcoin-btc-drop-fueled-by-deepseek-ai-shakeup-spurs-doubts-over-crypto-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 02:36:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>预算借款减少或将为印度现金流刺激添彩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/indian-bonds-poised-to-rally-further-on-borrowing-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度的净借款额可能连续第二年下降，这有可能延续该国债券的上涨势头，因为预计政府将坚持其财政整顿路径。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/indian-bonds-poised-to-rally-further-on-borrowing-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 01:37:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将关税威胁重新提上议程，美元上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/dollar-climbs-as-bessent-trump-reignite-universal-tariff-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普和财政部长的言论引发人们对关税谈判的短暂喘息已经真正结束的担忧后，美元兑所有主要货币均走强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/dollar-climbs-as-bessent-trump-reignite-universal-tariff-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 23:38:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员评估特朗普威胁和利比亚风险，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-28</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员权衡美国总统唐纳德·特朗普最近提高贸易关税的威胁，以及利比亚主要港口原油供应面临的风险，油价在周一下跌近 2% 之后小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-28</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 23:33:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言征收“更大”关税，美元上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示希望实施“更大”的普遍关税，美元随之上涨。由于对人工智能行业高估值的担忧持续到第二天，大多数亚洲股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 22:48:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度储备银行流动性措施导致印度债券收益率跌至三年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/india-central-bank-takes-steps-to-boost-cash-via-bond-buy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行的现金注入计划引发了人们对最早下周降息的希望，随后印度债券和股票出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/india-central-bank-takes-steps-to-boost-cash-via-bond-buy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 12:27:04 GMT</pubDate>
